Table oms.FinanceController2TaxTypeDefDO

Tax type naming as used by finance controllers (debtor management systems) instead of defaults.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id integer PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
FinanceControllerDO financeControllerRef integer The finance controller the name should be used for. 
financeControllerTaxTypeExportName varchar(512) NOT_NULL The name of the tax type used for exports to the finance controller. Used for export of open amounts, sales order or purchase orders. Example FullTax 
financeControllerTaxTypeImportName varchar(512) NOT_NULL The name of the tax type used for imports from the finance controller. Used for import of open amounts, sales order or purchase orders. Example FullTax 
TaxTypeDefDO taxTypeDefRef integer The tax type the name of the finance controller should be used for.
